videos.description: Gardner Minshew II returns to Washington State sporting a tight pair of jean shorts as the Cougars are set to square off against UCLA.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Minshew Mania rocks jorts in return to Washington State) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Minshew Mania rocks jorts in return to Washington State

videos.description: UCLA jumps on top of Washington State within the first two minutes on Dorian Thompson-Robinson's 14-yard touchdown to Joshua Kelley.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCLA strikes quickly on Thompson-Robinson's TD toss) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA strikes quickly on Thompson-Robinson's TD toss

videos.description: Washington State caps off a nine-play, 75-yard drive on Anthony Gordon's touchdown toss to Easop Winston Jr.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Washington State QB Gordon zips TD to Winston) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Washington State QB Gordon zips TD to Winston

videos.description: Demetric Felton cuts UCLA's deficit to four points as he takes a kick return all the way back to the house for a 100-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCLA's Felton houses kick return for 100-yard TD) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA's Felton houses kick return for 100-yard TD

videos.description: Anthony Gordon completes his fourth touchdown of the half and third to Easop Winston Jr. to pad Washington State's lead over UCLA.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gordon tosses 4th TD of half) 2019/9/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gordon tosses 4th TD of half

videos.description: Dorian Thompson-Robinson zips a quick pass to Demetric Felton, who turns on the burners for a 94-yard touchdown, his second long score of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Felton breaks free for 94-yard UCLA TD) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Felton breaks free for 94-yard UCLA TD

videos.description: Anthony Gordon breaks Gardner Minshew II's Washington State touchdown record with his eighth of the game and fourth to Easop Winston Jr.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gordon breaks Minshew’s TD record with 8th of game) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gordon breaks Minshew's TD record with 8th of game

videos.description: UCLA fights all the way back to take a lead over Washington State as Kyle Philips takes a punt back 69 yards for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCLA erases 32-point deficit, takes lead on PR TD) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA erases 32-point deficit, takes lead on PR TD

videos.description: Anthony Gordon tacks another score to his school record with his 9th touchdown of the game, this one for 69 yards to Max Borghi.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gordon strikes again with 9th TD pass) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gordon strikes again with 9th TD pass

videos.description: Dorian Thompson-Robinson finds Demetric Felton for his 5th touchdown pass of the day, giving UCLA a 67-63 lead late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCLA completes historic comeback on Thompson-Robinson's 5th TD) 2019/9/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA completes historic comeback on Thompson-Robinson's 5th TD

videos.description: Chip Kelly takes pride in how his Bruins have responded to a tough schedule and their resilience in battling back to defeat Washington State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_Interview (Kelly is proud of young UCLA team for comeback win) 2019/09/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kelly is proud of young UCLA team for comeback win

videos.description: UCLA negates a nine-touchdown performance by Washington State's Anthony Gordon with the third-biggest comeback in FBS history, overcoming a 32-point deficit to win 67-63.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (UCLA overcomes Gordon's 9 TDs in historic comeback win) 2019/9/21 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: UCLA overcomes Gordon's nine TDs in historic comeback win
